Interface DiffNode

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Cloneable
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    InternalNode
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultDiffNode, DefaultInternalNode, TestComponentTree.TestDefaultInternalNode

    public interface DiffNode
extends Cloneable
    A lightweight representation of a layout node, used to cache measurements between two Layout tree calculations.
